he security forces and police.<br />\n<br />\nThe toll of 1,500 is significantly higher than figures from international human rights groups and the United States. A Dec. 16 report by Amnesty International said the death toll was at least 304. The U.S. State Department, in a statement to Reuters, said it estimates that many hundreds of Iranians were killed, and has seen reports that number could be over 1,000.</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-iran-protests-specialreport/special-report-irans-leader-ordered-crackdown-on-unrest-do-whatever-it-takes-to-end-it-idUSKBN1YR0QR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-iran-protests-specialreport%2Fspecial-report-irans-leader-ordered-crackdown-on-unrest-do-whatever-it-takes-to-end-it-idUSKBN1YR0QR&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlptekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=8c08e2ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-iran-protests-specialreport%2Fspecial-report-irans-leader-ordered-crackdown-on-unrest-do-whatever-it-takes-to-end-it-idUSKBN1YR0QR&h=c8cf7450\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-iran-protests-specialreport/special-report-irans-leader-ordered-crackdown-on-unrest-do-whatever-it-takes-to-end-it-idUSKBN1YR0QR</a>"},{"pid":"6d0ccc56efb13459bab3e22757372d0a659adbeb","tid":1795198,"uid":8745,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae3c649025737c9bf1ad041182b22671090bc8a6","tid":1795198,"uid":84363,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4a4564cd486e6d8e2cb80d7fc1a72398cb01ad25","tid":1795198,"uid":112622,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c569fc0e72056f105596a206023bcfeebb21885f","tid":1795198,"uid":84363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:23:25.000Z","msg":"真64"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:26:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"但竟然死左1500個人都冇人理"},"citedBy":1,"